<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7889772f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s237"><num value="237">§ 237.</num><heading> Standard barrels for lime</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is established a large and a small barrel of lime, the large barrel to consist of two hundred and eighty pounds and the small barrel to consist of one hundred and eighty pounds, net weight.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78897730-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/act/1916-08-23/ch396/s1">Aug. 23, 1916, ch. 396, § 1</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/39/530">39 Stat. 530</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
